  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ne koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> ni <span class=\"highlighted-text\">does</span> za postavljanje pitanja tokom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">present simple</span>.</p>\n<p>Koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> zajedno sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">you</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">we</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">they</span>. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Do you like pizza?</span> (pitati za preferencije).</p>\n<p>Koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">does</span> zajedno sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">he</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">it</span>. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Does he work in an office?</span> (pitajte za njegovu funkciju).</p>\n<p>Zapamti, nakon <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">does</span>, glagol ostaje u svojoj osnovnoj formi (nema <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-s</span>).</p>\n</section>",
